{"article_id":"o438AWB7SsUrOkKf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. and other key figures","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"involved in an infamous Trump Tower meeting with Russian figures during the heat of the 2016 presidential campaign","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"largely downplayed its significance","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Hillary Clinton was hardly discussed","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"despite past speculation ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"in newly released transcripts from Senate Judiciary Committee interviews .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The committee released more than 1,800 pages of transcripts Wednesday from interviews with numerous figures","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"involved in the June 9 , 2016 meeting at Trump Tower .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"The controversial meeting ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"when it was revealed ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"fueled allegations of Trump campaign coordination with Russia","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"- as Trump Jr. was apparently promised dirt on Clinton ' s supposed involvement with Russia .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"But Trump Jr. said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"he was `` skeptical ''","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"going into the meeting with Russian lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"\" In his e-mail to me , Rob","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"[ Goldstone ]","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"suggested","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"that someone had official documents and information","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"that would incriminate Hillary Clinton and her dealings with Russia","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"and that the information would be very useful to the campaign , \"","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Trump Jr. said ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"he was \" skeptical of his outreach \"","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"as he only knew Goldstone as a \" colorful music promoter . \"","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Rob Goldstone ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"who was a music promoter ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"arranged the meeting at the request of pop singer Emin Agalarov ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"and later said","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"he thought","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"the meeting was a `` bad idea . ''","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"\" My skepticism was justified .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The meeting provided no meaningful information","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and turned out to be not about what was represented , \"","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"Trump Jr. said .","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"\" The meeting was instead primarily focused on Russian adoptions ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"which is exactly what I said over a year later in my statement of July 8 , 2017 . \"","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"In a written response , Veselnitskaya said","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"no information specific to Clinton was provided in the meeting .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"She also lamented the \" kind of apocalyptic Hollywood scenario what a private conversation between a lawyer and a businessman can be turned into . \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Trump Jr. testified","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"that he had \" no way","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"to gauge \" the \" reliability , credibility , or accuracy \" of anything","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Goldstone promised .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"\" I love it , \"","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Trump Jr. had written back to Goldstone at the time .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"But he testified","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that it was \" simply a colloquial way","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"of saying","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that I appreciated Rob ' s gesture . \"","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Trump Jr. testified","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"if he was given information on Clinton ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he would have then consulted with counsel","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"to \" make an informed decision","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"as to whether to give it any further consideration . \"","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"\" I also note","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"at this time","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"there was no focus on Russian activities","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that there is today , \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Trump Jr. said .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Trump Jr. also noted","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that he was not aware of who would be in the meeting .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that Veselnitskaya did not provide any information on Clinton beyond \" very generally something about individuals","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"connected to Russia","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"supporting or funding Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton or the Democratic National Committee . ''","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"When asked how the meeting ended ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Trump Jr. testified","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that \" we went our separate ways","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and Rob Goldstone came up to me","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"and apologized . \"","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"\" Essentially he apologized for what","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"he believed","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"was wasting our time , \"","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"Trump Jr. said .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Trump Jr. was also asked","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"whether he believed","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Goldstone \" duped \" him into a meeting under \" false pretenses \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"to \" grab \" his attention .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"\" I imagine","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"there was an element of showmanship involved , yes , \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Trump Jr. replied .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"In addition to Trump Jr. , the committee interviewed four other people","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"who attended the Trump Tower meeting in New York","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"-- publicist Goldstone ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"who set up the meeting with the promise of dirt on Clinton ;","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Rinat Akhmetshin , a prominent Russian-American lobbyist ; Ike Kaveladze , a business associate of a Moscow-based developer , and a translator .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"The panel was also not able to interview Jared Kushner , Trump 's son-in-law , or Paul Manafort , Trump 's former campaign manager ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"even though both attended the Trump Tower meeting .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"But the committee released a short page of notes","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Manafort took on his phone during the meeting .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The White House has said","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"the president was involved","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"in drafting an initial statement","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"after news of the meeting broke last year .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The statement said","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"the meeting primarily concerned a Russian adoption program ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"though Trump Jr. later released the emails","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"showing","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"he agreed to the sit-down","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"after he was promised information on Clinton .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"The emails also show","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"he accepted the meeting","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"despite it being described as part of a Russian government effort","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"to aid his father 's campaign .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Asked in the interview","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"if his father was involved in drafting the statement ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"`` I do n't know .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"I never spoke to my father about it . ''","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Trump Jr. also stressed","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that he did not tell his father about the meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"`` I would n't have wasted his time with it . ''","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Trump Jr. also told the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"that he could n't remember","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"whether he had discussed the Russia investigation as a whole with his father ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"according to transcripts .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"He also said","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"he did n't think","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"there was anything wrong","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"with attending the Trump Tower meeting .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Like Trump Jr. and Kushner ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"who released a public statement about the meeting last year ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Goldstone said","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"the meeting was disappointing .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"he reported back to Emin Agalarov","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"that `` this was the most embarrassing thing","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"you 've ever asked me to do .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"I 've just sat in a meeting about adoption . ''","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"The meeting is under scrutiny in Special Counsel Robert Mueller 's Russia investigation .","depth":3},{"id":134,"text":"The testimony of Fusion GPS co-founder Glenn Simpson was also made public Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"-- for a second time .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"His testimony was first released , unilaterally , by Committee Ranking Member Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , in January .","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"Simpson 's firm was behind the composition of the Trump dossier ,","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"filled with salacious , and unverified , allegations against the president","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"regarding matters","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"related to Russia .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"Despite Fox News ' past reporting","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"that Simpson was with Veselnitskaya before and after the Trump Tower meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"Simpson said in testimony","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"that he was n't aware of the meeting beforehand ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"and was `` stunned ''","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"to later learn about it .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Trump Jr. testified","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"that at the time of the Trump Tower meeting , he `` had never heard of Glenn Simpson or Fusion GPS . '","depth":6},{"id":149,"text":"' \" Americans rightly have many questions about this meeting ,","depth":4},{"id":150,"text":"and today , we are releasing the transcripts and exhibits from interviews","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"we ' ve conducted","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"to allow the public to know","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"what we know , ''","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , said in a statement .","depth":3},{"id":155,"text":"`` These materials ,","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"taken in their entirety ,","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"provide the most complete public picture of the events","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"surrounding the meeting to date .","depth":5},{"id":159,"text":"Americans can now review this unfiltered information","depth":4},{"id":160,"text":"and arrive at their own conclusions . \"","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":321,"left":309,"right":320,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":293,"right":308,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":244,"right":292,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":173,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":169,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":167,"right":168,"relation":"elabora